Tech Ops Mobility  iPad Pin Change 1. Open Settings and click on Touch ID and Passcode.  
 2. Enter the device’s Current Passcode.  
 3. Select  Change Passcode. 
 

 
Tech Ops Mobility 4. Enter your Old/Current Passcode. 
 5. Enter your New/Desired Passcode and click Next. NOTE: This can be either numeric or alpha numeric by clicking Passcode Options. 
 6. Enter the New Passcode again to verify and click Done.
